"Worm.io" for Chrome Extension is an exciting and addictive snake game that can be played for free on the website https://googlesnake.org/. In this game, your goal is to survive and dominate the arena by outlasting your opponents and devouring them.

As a worm, you navigate through the level, collecting pellets to grow in size and strength. The more pellets you consume, the longer your worm becomes. Your ultimate aim is to become the top worm on the leaderboard, showcasing your skill and dominance.


Visit https://googlesnake.org/ and dive into the thrilling world of "Worm.io" for Chrome Extension. Conquer the leaderboard, dominate the arena, and prove your worth as the top worm in this fast-paced and strategic snake game. Enjoy the challenge and have fun!
